data.description: If you are looking for a beautiful updated house, your search stops here. Come and see this wonderful 4-bedroom and 4-bathroom house with an attached garage. Updated kitchen with updated Vinyl wood flooring. You will see an ample-size kitchen with an updated granite counter, stainless steel appliances, and updated cabinets. The kitchen leads to the gorgeous living room. The second level has four great-sized bedrooms. The lower level provides more options for living spaces to use as family room, office, guest space, or play space. The kitchen, windows, and bathrooms have all been updated in the last few years. The house has a solar System that was installed a few years ago.  A huge backyard to enjoy outside and entertain yourself. Come and see it before it's gone!
